<br>
Infiltrators and archers: Want evade penalty vs DW reamoved, I can undrestand scouts (2 penalties, I would give them parry and more spec points) but not the other.<br>
<br>
Too many whines vs DW and which class would suffer more if penalties are removed? Mercenary.<br>
<br>
Arms Tl is pushing to remove double spec in order to give offensive arms more parry. None complain about 2H reducing parry. No one seems to notice that DW classes in each realm double specs too (except Savages). I feel like everyone wants us to be rp cow.<br>
<br>
Your opinion?<br>
