<br>
It seems the Warrior TL doesn't know, either, becasue he said that to balance things out for Vs-Evade, 1H should get a bonud against dodger classes.<br>
<br>
Personaly, I say screw 'em all. I've duelled S-S people and only hit them once, I've been OOE and hitting Paladins consistently and STILL seen their HP grow back faster than I could take it off.<br>
<br>
Hmm, but I don't really want Albion's battery nerfed <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  After all, they are always complaining about doing no real damage, which is true.<br>
<br>
Armsman getting more points? Pray tell, what's wrong with any of these specs:<br>
<br>
50pole, 50slash, 28parry<br>
50pole, 39slash, 41parry (yes, possible!)<br>
50pole, 40slash, 42shield<br>
50shield, 50slash, 28parry<br>
42shield, 50slash, 37parry<br>
<br>
What beautiful variation, and all pretty damn offensive IMHO. Would that the mercenary had such a magnitude of choices <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Pallys should likewise have to spend more points if they want to be slam-chanting-2H offensive hybrids, though perhaps they should get Str as a seconday stat and not Peity (egk!).<br>
