<br>
Shield users give up a ton of offensive and honestly aren't rewarded with enough defensive to break even. With current RvR seeing a flavour of the month rise in dual wielding tanks (Specifically Savages, which honestly still need to be nerfed into the dirt), Shield users are getting left out in the cold. A defensive tanks job is to defend, but with so many dual wielders running around in the current system, Guard just doesn't work that well. This is an emerging problem from Midgard though mainly...all 3 of the original light tanks are fine, its that 4th bastard child thats the problem. -.-<br>
